                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>No. 46 South Street</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Mr dear <addressee>Mr Leeser</addressee></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I was very glad to see<lb/> your <sic>autography</sic> again and\n                    <add>?</add> your<lb/> note of <date>7</date> inst with great pleasure as I<lb/>\n                now welcome you home again. I am<lb/> also very glad that you return in\n                improved<lb/> health and that your <sic>visitings</sic> have not<lb/> proved\n                unsuccessful pecuniarily</p>\n            <p>I intended to write to our mutual and<lb/> good friend <persName>Mr.\n                    Cozens</persName> during your<lb/> absence and am heartily sorry that<lb/> I did\n                not, but somehow time slips by<lb/> so rapidly that it comes and goes before<lb/> I\n                am aware of it. However I hope to do bet-<lb/>ter next time. My health has bee\n                un-<lb/>commonly good during the winter and<lb/> is so now but I fear for the next\n                few<lb/> months, particularly as I am so situated<lb/> that I do not see how I can\n                get away<lb/> from home. I had such a delightful</p>"
                  },
